---
title: Aromatic Soy Glazed Beef Strips with chilli and scattered scallion
description: Succulent beef strips are coated in a sweet and tangy glaze in this Asian-fusion stir-fry dish. Fluffy rice and chilli for bite round out a hearty and flavourful meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R16_W07_IE_IECB20967-2_Main_high-15118310.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/6571b2ce2db9273db6a47bb3.pdf
